'''Islgan n umussu''' n [[Isaac Newton|Isḥaq Nyuṭun]] ar skaren azday inger afud da ismussun tazzit d umussu nns.

==Aslgn amzwaru ==
Ar ittini uslgn amzwaru n Nyutun mas ig yat tazzit t-bidd ur attmussu neɣ ar tmussu s yat tazzla timzgit g yan umnid, ira tɣama tazzit ad tɣama tbidd neɣ ra-tɣama tssuda s yat tazzla timzgit mqqar ar fllas ittagez wafud. Aslgn ad i-tt-uyssan s wassaɣ n '''Aslgn n Tussimt <ref>Amawal n Tasengama (Tafizikt) :  https://amaruyidir.files.wordpress.com/2019/09/amawal_amatu_n_tfizikt_tatrart_tafransist-taqbaylit-dc3a9verrouillc3a9.pdf, Tasna tiss 38</ref>'''.

Rad tt nara s ɣmk-ad:

<math>\sum \vec{F} = 0\; \Leftrightarrow\; {dv \over dt} = 0.</math>

'''Aslgn n Tussimt''' iwfat g tizwiri mass [[Galilyu Galili]] yara-t s tɣarast nna s t-nssen, macc ɣir i wmussu afraran f wakal, g yan uzmz yaḍni mass [[Runi Dikart]] issmɣur aslgn ad.

Dat  [[Galilyu Galili|Galili]] tella yat tswingmt mas akk imussuten ifrarann darsen timntal tusridin. Macc [[Galilyu Galili|Galili]] iẓẓdar a-ysan seg irimen-ns mas tazzit ittmussun, ra-tɣama ar tmussu mqqar yan afud ar iswwuri bac a tbidd.

==Aslgn wiss sin ==
'''Aslgn wiss sin''' n [[Isḥaqq Nyutun|Nyutun]] iga yan uslgn yakkan yan uglam asmktan n maf-iẓdar yan wafud at isker i wmussu n yat tazzit. ar ittini mas asnfel n tasmkta n umussu g uzmz n yat tazzit inict g umnad d tasmkta i tazduzt (mass) d tazzla-ns. tasmkta n umussu tga zund tazzla, gan imawayen <ref> Amawal n Tusnakt : http://adrar-inu.blogspot.com/2015/04/lexique-de-mathematiques-amawal-n.html</ref>, darsen ssin tasmkta d amnid. 

Afud i-tt-ssurḥen f yat tazzit iẓdar ayssnfel tasmkta n umussu ns, neɣ amnad ns ne iẓdar atn issnfel ssin. Aslgn wiss sin n [[Isḥaqq Nyutun|Nyutun]] iga yan uslgn akk istawhmman g [[Tasengama]].

Yat tazzit ilan yat tazduzt timzgit <math>m</math>, ras nara  : 

<big><math display="inline">\overrightarrow{F} = m \times \overrightarrow{a} </math></big>   neɣ nẓdar at nara s tɣarast yaḍnin :  <math>\overrightarrow{F} =m \times \frac{d\overrightarrow{v}}{dt}  </math>

Ɣid ar nmmal :

*''<math>\overrightarrow{F}</math>  : Afud''
*''<math>m </math>  : Tazduzt''
*''<math>\overrightarrow{a}</math>  : Tazzazt''
Maɣ''' <math>\overrightarrow{F}</math>''' d '''<math>\overrightarrow{a}</math>''' gan imawayen.

Ig yat tazzit dars afud agnsan,ar ittazzaz s mklli aɣ ttini tagda n uslgn ad wiss ssin n Nyutun. seg tasga yaḍnin ig tazzit ur attazzaz, ur ra-gis ili yan afud agnsan.

==Aslgn wiss kraḍ ==
[[Afaylu:Skaters showing newtons third law.svg|thumb|Tawlaft immaln Aslgn wiss krad n Nyutun]]
Aslgn wiss kraḍ n Nyutun ar ittini mas ig darneɣ snat tazziwin, yat ar iṭṭiḍiṣ f wayyaḍ, nẓdar anini mas yan ar issḥruy afud f wayyaḍ s tmkta inicten d imnaden isniln. Aslgn wiss kraḍ ittuyssan s wassaɣ n '''Aslgn n tigawt d trarit<ref>Amawal Tamaziɣt-Takatalunit :  http://www.amazic.cat/dictionary/reaccio/</ref>. '''Aslgn ad istawhmma bahra g tiɣri n amyas agellal'''.'''

